description: This spacious East Side condo, offering a bright, open floor plan  truly has it all! Perfect for modern living and entertaining, the sun-filled living room features a gas fireplace, defined dining area, and a well-appointed kitchen w/leathered granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, pot filler, wine fridge, and plenty of cabinet & closet space. The primary suite offers a peaceful retreat w/a walk-in closet, direct access to a private deck w/a gas line for grilling, and an en-suite marble bath complete with a steam shower. The oversized guest bedroom features double closets and comfortably fits a queen bed & desk. Tasteful updates & fresh paint throughout gives the home a crisp, move-in-ready feel. Additional highlights include crown molding, central air,  in-unit laundry, exclusive-use locked storage, and TWO full deeded parking spaces. Located in a professionally managed, pet-friendly, owner-occupied association near the beach, bus lines, and all that Southie has to offer!
